name: Ruin 2017 - Daniel Jerome
description:
Choreography made in 2017. Video art present day. Reminiscing a bit of my old life. This was 2017 when the chronic pain in my body was starting to get worse, but I kept fighting past it and taking on jobs still during my professional dance career.
